From Zauberer Subject Re locking lugnuts tire rebalance In article writes If you put a locking lugnut on your tires do you need to have your tires rebalanced John Mas E Mail Address MAS I bought a set of ARE's a few months back and decided to add locks so that I could keep my new I haven't had a balance problem yet so I assume that it might be just particular to your type of stock My rims were balanced with new BFG T A's at a speed shop to the finest setting on their machine so that helps Zauberer Travis